		"description": {
			"value": "<p>This spell only affects constructs, objects, and vehicles.</p><p><strong>Healing</strong></p><ul><li><p>Target gains hit points equal to 2d10 + your spellcasting ability modifier.*</p></li><li><p>You can also reattach a missing piece of a construct, object, or vehicle if you have the same piece (or a replacement piece).</p></li><li><p>If the target is a nonliving construct, object, or vehicle that was destroyed or killed, you can restore it to functionality if you have all the pieces.**</p></li></ul><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Increase healing by 2d10 for each spell level above 1st.</p><p><em>**This does not revive player characters with the construct ancestry or other constructs with a soul, who need a <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.6yixBp8pwhVAkbUJ]{revivify}</em> spell instead.</em></p>",
